org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.impl.mtReactors

Class IsolationInbox

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.impl.mtReactors.Inbox
      • org.agilewiki.jactor2.core.impl.mtReactors.IsolationInbox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class IsolationInbox
extends Inbox
    The inbox used by IsolationReactor, the next request is not made available for processing until a result is assigned to the previous request. This is implemented using two ArrayDeques as the doLocal queues, one for requests and the other for events and responses.
